            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1586430722295-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, combine a squeeze of<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>lemon</strong> <strong>juice</strong> with your<strong> mayo</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>lemony mayo</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
